    LocDescriptions:
    - _name: FR
      Language: 0
      Txt: "Toutes tes actions <sprite name=heal> et <sprite name=revive> co\xFBtent
        1 <sprite name=action_point> de moins."
    - _name: EN
      Language: 1
      Txt: 'Target yourself a friendly unit in contact that is not engaged in melee
        combat.

        One heal costs 1AP and allow you to roll a die that heals
        1HP if you get a success result.

        If you target a troop, no miniature
        can come back to the battlefield thanks to this gear. Only a hurt miniature
        may be healed.

        A unit cannot receive more than 2 heals in a single
        activation.


        /!\ HEROES only'
    ExportString: ':white_large_square:'
